<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idb8163fe9-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s1304"><num value="1304">§ 1304.</num><heading> Reservation of right to amend or repeal</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The right to alter, amend, or repeal any provision of this chapter is hereby reserved to the Congress.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idb8163fea-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/act/1935-08-14/ch531">Aug. 14, 1935, ch. 531</ref>, title XI, § 1104, <ref href="/us/stat/49/648">49 Stat. 648</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
